  "detailed_description": "<strong>Unite the Overworld</strong><br>Experience an epic legend from the Minecraft universe and the Overworld as you’ve never seen it before.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928870/extras/fb650f3ed0f1adbe4647ec3e20a5dd00.poster.avif?t=1746133966\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928870/extras/fb650f3ed0f1adbe4647ec3e20a5dd00.webm?t=1746133966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928870/extras/fb650f3ed0f1adbe4647ec3e20a5dd00.mp4?t=1746133966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Epic Battles</strong><br>Form alliances with new friends and familiar mobs, then lead the charge in epic battles against the fierce piglins to defend the Overworld.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928870/extras/f374b1af0d925a4903fe116438af8f51.poster.avif?t=1746133966\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928870/extras/f374b1af0d925a4903fe116438af8f51.webm?t=1746133966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928870/extras/f374b1af0d925a4903fe116438af8f51.mp4?t=1746133966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>A vivid Overworld</strong><br>Traverse a lush, dynamic world that’s rich in resources and different in each playthrough.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1928870/extras/21d1af8561ea9772f131c4a30005dedd.poster.avif?t=1746133966\" width=600 height=100 ><source 